Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if he's going to{\i0}\N{\i1}skip school again today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,SHINJI'S ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, get up. How long are you\Ngonna stay home from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five days already.\NUnit 01 is as good as new.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Its pilot shouldn't be\Nsitting around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,TO MS. MISATO KATSURAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away. I guess I can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class as Mr. Ikari.\NOur names are Aida and Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida and Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Yes, ma'am! I'm Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, aren't you the two\Nwho got into Unit 01's entry plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am! We're really sorry\Nfor any trouble we caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, we were worried because\NShinji hasn't been to school since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so we thought we'd check in on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Shinji's at Nerv's\Ntraining facility right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, these study guides\Nhave been piling up on his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to\Ncome all this way. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we should be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hi to Mr. Ikari for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll do that. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you little idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,TOKYO-3 LOOP LINE NO. 7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next stop is Nagao-touge, Nagao-touge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please exit on the right side{\i0}\N{\i1}of the train.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for using{\i0}\N{\i1}Tokyo-3 Loop Line No. 7.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This train is no longer in service{\i0}\N{\i1}after this stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please remember to collect{\i0}\N{\i1}your belongings before exiting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy! Step right in!\NIt's a real bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-You really couldn't detect it?!{\i0}\N{\i1}-No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An object tens of millimeters across{\i0}\N{\i1}struck the South Pole at speeds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in excess of 10% of the speed of light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was beyond modern science's ability{\i0}\N{\i1}to predict, much less prevent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But look at what's happening outside!{\i0}\N{\i1}What good is science?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Atmospheric flux caused by axial shift{\i0}\N{\i1}has decreased to 3%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has it gotten better outside, then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! There's a tsunami on the way!{\i0}\N{\i1}Incoming at 230 meters per second!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor! We must escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, my duty is to stay here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, dying is easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you also have a duty{\i0}\N{\i1}to bear witness to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He {\i0}is{\i1} only 14 years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Placing the fate of the human race\Non his shoulders is a lot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but to have 14-year-olds pilot the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, any word from Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,None. Maybe he's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you intend to do about it?\N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be better off\Nif he didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after the last battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ignore my order?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Aren't I your operations director?\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your duty to obey my orders.\NDo you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't let this happen again.\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really getting through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, just repeating\N"Yes, ma'am" isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But why does it matter? We won.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It might feel easier to just superficially\Nplay along with what others say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but piloting an Eva with that attitude\Nwill get you killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say that I'm glad\Nto hear you've got guts,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're way off base if you think\Nthat will score you points, Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not fishing for compliments.\NI'm just the only one who can pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If piloting the Eva only brings him pain,\Nhe's better off not piloting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida, go on without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't leave you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The new kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,SUMMER TRAINING OVERVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohji was sorry he hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear his little sister chewed him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it was your robot\Nthat saved us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hilarious that he got taken\Ndown a peg by a grade-schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it at night.\NThose cicadas aren't buzzing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice and quiet when I was little,\Nbut there's more every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato said something about\Nthe ecosystem rebuilding itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ms. Misato," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You live with a total babe\Nand you get to pilot that Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could pilot the Evangelion\Nall by myself just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't if I were you.\NYour mother would be worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not a problem.\NI don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're hungry, right?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do this a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it training for guerrilla warfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would toys like this do?\NI'm just having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with Nerv Security & Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking you to HQ under section eight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Safety Preservation Ordinance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Will you comply?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you just stood there{\i0}\N{\i1}and let them grab him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. Those guys were\NNerv Security & Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that got to do with it?!\NDon't you have any balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gross!\N-Weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an idiot picks a fight he can't win.\NBalls don't enter into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's been a while.\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Has wandering around for the last two days\Nmade you feel any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Eva is ready and waiting.\NWill you pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to scold me\Nfor running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you wouldn't. You're not family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen with Unit 01\Nif I didn't pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose Rei would pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I do something like that?\NI couldn't force it all on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NI'm not cut out for this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you and Ayanami and Ms. Ritsuko--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!\NWhat others think doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't really want to, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the Evas and everything else!\NGo back to your old life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep acting like this,\Nyou're more trouble than you're worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Children\Nwill leave Tokyo-3 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then rewrite Unit 01's data to match Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of Unit 00's\Nreactivation trial results,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we will press on with trials with Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Reports from the Marduk Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,indicate the Fourth Children\Nhas not been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning that we have\Nno replacement pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where is Ms. Misato?\NI'd like to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer with Nerv.\NYou're not cleared for that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Ikari!\N-You forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohji, out with it! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, I shouldn't have hit you twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I wouldn't be able\Nto live with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how melodramatic he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, if it helps bury the hatchet,\Njust hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You don't have much time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let me have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did you know I'd be here?\N-Call it a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've said goodbye to dozens\Nof classmates here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't stick around, we'll all\Nprobably have to leave town eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't force you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw what it's like for you in that Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare anybody to bad-mouth you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat the crap out of the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that hangdog look, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take care.\N-Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be clobbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dishonest! And a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sneak... and a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give us any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hedgehog's Dilemma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The closer they get,\Nthe more they hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He talks like that because he doesn't\Nknow how else to express his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Limited express maglev bound for Atsugi{\i0}\N{\i1}now arriving on track two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your safety,{\i0}\N{\i1}please stand behind the yellow line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train on track two{\i0}\N{\i1}is an official-use train{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}departing for Atsugi at 4:20.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The public must remain behind the fence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also, the boarding of unauthorized{\i0}\N{\i1}personnel is strictly forbidden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take extra care to obey these rules.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep it up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the babe from Ikari's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Local train bound for Goura{\i0}\N{\i1}now arriving on track four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your safety,{\i0}\N{\i1}please stand behind the yellow line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Passengers with small children,{\i0}\N{\i1}please keep a close eye on them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train arriving on track four{\i0}\N{\i1}is the 4:32 local train for Goura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All passengers using this train{\i0}\N{\i1}should board and wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Train now arriving.{\i0}\N{\i1}Please step behind the yellow line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei Ayanami leads a life where her{\i0}\N{\i1}interactions with others are minimal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Commander Ikari is the only one{\i0}\N{\i1}she opens up to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji is perplexed by this girl who{\i0}\N{\i1}is closer to his own father than he is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "Rei, Beyond the Heart".{\i0}
